 my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4706246-dfi-retail-a-beneficiary-of-health-and-convenience-trends-rating-upgrade\">July 24, 2024, article</a> touched on the favorable growth outlook for DFILF's \"convenience</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747464-dfi-retail-sales-make-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:17:35", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747463", "title": "Funko: Easy Money Has Been Made; Time To Downgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Row of figures of American company Funko Pop in the shop window\" data-id=\"961973282\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1082px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">kipgodi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In a perfect world, investment opportunities would be perpetually attractive and would generate strong returns all the time. But that's not how this world works. Even the best prospects eventually achieve their easy upside, leaving more limited upside on the table. And if</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747463-funko-easy-money-made-time-to-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:10:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747462", "title": "Dollar Tree Stores: Short-Term Concerns But Still A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar Tree\" data-id=\"1265347025\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5886px\" height=\"3924px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment summary</h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4704509-dollar-tree-stay-calm-and-remain-long-on-this-strong-operator\">previous investment thought</a> on Dollar Tree Stores (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLTR\" title=\"Dollar Tree, Inc.\">DLTR</a></span>) (published on 17th July) was a buy rating because I believed it provided investors good exposure to the uncertain macro conditions back then, and that valuation was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747462-dollar-tree-stores-short-term-concerns-but-still-a-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:02:43", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747367", "title": "2 Places To Put Your Money If The Fed Raises Rates In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"2025 spelled with golden numerals and zero is replaced with a piggy bank\" data-id=\"2183192528\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Since the Fed lowered interest rates last month by another 25 basis points, the overall market has seemingly not agreed with that decision. Uncertainty within the bond markets has caused the 2-year and 10-year treasuries to experience volatility. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747367-2-places-to-put-your-money-if-the-fed-raises-rates-in-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:47:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747458", "title": "Royal Caribbean Cruises: Why You Should Disembark", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Royal Caribbean, Navigator of the Seas cruise ship and tender boat\" data-id=\"1712186363\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sanfel/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I give Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RCL\" title=\"Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.\">RCL</a></span>) a sell rating because the company has poor short-term liquidity, a massive amount of long-term debt, and is overvalued by 227% from its current intrinsic value of $70.48, much of which is due to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747458-royal-caribbean-cruises-why-you-should-disembark", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:38:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747353", "title": "TKO Group: WWE Evolution Continues With Netflix Shift", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"WWE World Wrestling Entertainment American professional fake wrestling promotion company headquarters in Stamford Connecticut.\" data-id=\"2163043433\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1068px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yuriy T</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>\u201cIn this industry, just like in life, everything evolves.\u201d</p></blockquote> <p>That was a quote from Paul \u201cTriple H\u201d Levesque from an episode of TKO Group's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TKO\" title=\"TKO Group Holdings, Inc.\">TKO</a></span>) <em>WWE</em> <em>Monday Night RAW </em>that aired in February 2003. At the time, Triple H was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747353-tko-group-wwe-evolution-continues-with-netflix-shift", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747457", "title": "BlackRock: Now Is Not The Time To Buy (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BlackRock Headquarters in New York\" data-id=\"1689041338\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1026px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">BlackRock's corporate headquarters in New York City, New York.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">georgeclerk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>For me, my dividend growth investing strategy is simple. I aim to own the most dominant players in massive and growing industries. This is because industry dominance is usually reflective of companies</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689041338/image_1689041338.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747457-blackrock-now-is-not-the-time-to-buy-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747456", "title": "PUTW: Solid Way To Add Flexibility To A Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female yoga student doing pose in yoga studio\" data-id=\"2155324534\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155324534/image_2155324534.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3